        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="am">
                <note>The following subdivision and incipits are taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient12034">London, British Library, BL Oriental 12034</ref>, quoted according to the
                    catalogue description in <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/RSEA4WPK"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary"/><title level="m">Catalogue of Ethiopian Manuscripts in the British Library acquired since the Year 1877</title><author><forename>Stefan</forename><surname>Strelcyn</surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>British Museum</publisher><date>1978</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note><citedRange unit="page">150</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Terenter">
                    <label>Against tǝrǝntǝr (?)</label>
                    <note>Possibly related to the disease indicated as <foreign xml:lang="am">tǝrrǝtǝr</foreign> in 
                        <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7T7W7L3J"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1968Medecine"/><title level="m">Médecine et plantes d’Éthiopie. Les traités médicaux éthiopiens. Medycyna i zioła etiopskie. Etiopskie traktaty medyczne</title><title level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Stefan</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Strelcyn</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Warszawa</pubPlace><publisher>Państwowe Wydawnictwo Naukowe</publisher><date>1968</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</t:title></series><biblScope unit="volume">XIV</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">381</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>&gt;የትርንትር፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Animals">
                    <label>For the animals</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ለእንስሳ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Abreq">
                    <label>Against ʾabrǝq</label>
                    <note>Prescription against <foreign xml:lang="am">አብርቅ፡</foreign> (contagious disease affecting livestock or horses), cf. 
                        <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7T7W7L3J"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1968Medecine"/><title level="m">Médecine et plantes d’Éthiopie. Les traités médicaux éthiopiens. Medycyna i zioła etiopskie. Etiopskie traktaty medyczne</title><title level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Stefan</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Strelcyn</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Warszawa</pubPlace><publisher>Państwowe Wydawnictwo Naukowe</publisher><date>1968</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</t:title></series><biblScope unit="volume">XIV</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">369</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ለአብርቅ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Qitten">
                    <label>Against syphilis (qiṭṭǝñ)</label>
                    <note>Against <foreign xml:lang="am">ቂጥኝ፡</foreign> (syphilis, venereal disease), cf. 
                        <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7T7W7L3J"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1968Medecine"/><title level="m">Médecine et plantes d’Éthiopie. Les traités médicaux éthiopiens. Medycyna i zioła etiopskie. Etiopskie traktaty medyczne</title><title level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Stefan</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Strelcyn</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Warszawa</pubPlace><publisher>Państwowe Wydawnictwo Naukowe</publisher><date>1968</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</t:title></series><biblScope unit="volume">XIV</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">515</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>የቂጥኝ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Madyat">
                    <label>Against madyāt</label>
                    <note>Prescription against <foreign xml:lang="am">ማድያት፡</foreign> (a skin disease), cf. 
                        <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7T7W7L3J"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1968Medecine"/><title level="m">Médecine et plantes d’Éthiopie. Les traités médicaux éthiopiens. Medycyna i zioła etiopskie. Etiopskie traktaty medyczne</title><title level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Stefan</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Strelcyn</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Warszawa</pubPlace><publisher>Państwowe Wydawnictwo Naukowe</publisher><date>1968</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</t:title></series><biblScope unit="volume">XIV</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">203</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ዘማድያት፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Gurguho">
                    <label>Against gʷǝrguho</label>
                    <note>Likely to be related to <foreign xml:lang="am">ጉርጎሖ፡</foreign> (an illness of the throat).</note>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>&gt;ዘጕርጉሆ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Cow">
                    <label>About the cow</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ዘላህም፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="AnyDisease">
                    <label>Against (any) disease</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ደዌ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Demon">
                    <label>Against a demon</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ጋኔን፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Andarabi">
                    <label>Against ʾAndarabbi</label>
                    <note>Prescription against <foreign xml:lang="am">አንደረቢ፡</foreign> (maleficent or evil force which popular belief credits
                        with being able to hurl objects through the air or to put sand, excrement, etc. in people's food), cf. 
                        <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7T7W7L3J"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1968Medecine"/><title level="m">Médecine et plantes d’Éthiopie. Les traités médicaux éthiopiens. Medycyna i zioła etiopskie. Etiopskie traktaty medyczne</title><title level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Stefan</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Strelcyn</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Warszawa</pubPlace><publisher>Państwowe Wydawnictwo Naukowe</publisher><date>1968</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</t:title></series><biblScope unit="volume">XIV</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">779</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>አንደረቢ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Wasfat">
                    <label>Against wasfāt</label>
                    <note>Prescription against <foreign xml:lang="am">ወስፋት፡</foreign> (intestinal worm), possibly related to
                        <foreign xml:lang="am">ወስፌ፡</foreign> / <foreign xml:lang="am">መስፌ፡</foreign> in 
                        <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7T7W7L3J"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1968Medecine"/><title level="m">Médecine et plantes d’Éthiopie. Les traités médicaux éthiopiens. Medycyna i zioła etiopskie. Etiopskie traktaty medyczne</title><title level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Stefan</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Strelcyn</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Warszawa</pubPlace><publisher>Państwowe Wydawnictwo Naukowe</publisher><date>1968</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</t:title></series><biblScope unit="volume">XIV</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">387, 405</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ወስፋት፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Tshenqur">
                    <label>Against č̣̣ǝnqur</label>
                    <note>Prescription against <foreign xml:lang="am">ጭንቁር፡</foreign> (yaws, cancer, chancre or gangrenous wound), cf.
                        <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7T7W7L3J"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1968Medecine"/><title level="m">Médecine et plantes d’Éthiopie. Les traités médicaux éthiopiens. Medycyna i zioła etiopskie. Etiopskie traktaty medyczne</title><title level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Stefan</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Strelcyn</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Warszawa</pubPlace><publisher>Państwowe Wydawnictwo Naukowe</publisher><date>1968</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</t:title></series><biblScope unit="volume">XIV</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">481, 483</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ጭንቁር፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Snake">
                    <label>Against a snake</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ለባብ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Shadows">
                    <label>Against enemies</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ለጽላት፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Qusl">
                    <label>About leprosy (qʷǝsla śǝgā)</label>
                    <note>Prescription to cure <foreign xml:lang="am">ቍስለ፡ ሥጋ፡</foreign> (leprosy), cf.
                        <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7T7W7L3J"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1968Medecine"/><title level="m">Médecine et plantes d’Éthiopie. Les traités médicaux éthiopiens. Medycyna i zioła etiopskie. Etiopskie traktaty medyczne</title><title level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Stefan</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Strelcyn</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Warszawa</pubPlace><publisher>Państwowe Wydawnictwo Naukowe</publisher><date>1968</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Prace Orientalistyczne</t:title></series><biblScope unit="volume">XIV</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">111</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ቍስለ፡ ሥጋ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography">
                
            </div>
        </body>
    </text></TEI>